{"tid":1283603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"譚詠麟鍾鎮濤美國開騷 網民促寫信FBI介入","createTime":"2019-07-04T00:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T03:28:34.000Z","uid":181557,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b2f9e89722e2ddb3ac1e856c95e163de2cebf37c","tid":1283603,"uid":181557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:36:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E8%AD%9A%E8%A9%A0%E9%BA%9F%E9%8D%BE%E9%8E%AE%E6%BF%A4%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%8B%E9%A8%B7-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E4%BF%83%E5%AF%AB%E4%BF%A1fbi%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5-178769\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E5%25A8%259B%25E6%25A8%2582%2F%25E8%25AD%259A%25E8%25A9%25A0%25E9%25BA%259F%25E9%258D%25BE%25E9%258E%25AE%25E6%25BF%25A4%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2596%258B%25E9%25A8%25B7-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%25AF%25AB%25E4%25BF%25A1fbi%25E4%25BB%258B%25E5%2585%25A5-178769&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=8b9a5f45\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/%E8%AD%9A%E8%A9%A0%E9%BA%9F%E9%8D%BE%E9%8E%AE%E6%BF%A4%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%96%8B%E9%A8%B7-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E4%BF%83%E5%AF%AB%E4%BF%A1fbi%E4%BB%8B%E5%85%A5-178769</a><br />\n<br />\n最近有網民發現二人稍後將到美國開騷，決意與友人發信去ICE(美國移民及海關執法局)及FBI(聯邦調查局)。該名網民寫道︰「我決定和朋友起草一份舉報信交去ICE同FBI，大意係呢兩條友公開支持黑警暴力對待示威者，與美國民主自由嘅價值有所抵觸，加上其立場親中共，佢哋身為知名人士，好有可能會對美國華裔進行影響甚至統戰。所以要求美國移民執法局同聯邦調查局審視佢哋嘅演出簽證。最好可以取消簽證。 如果封信寫好，我會po上嚟，大家一起舉報！！！」"},{"pid":"771d21ad26f740db3eb59719ce4dcc4b55fa68ef","tid":1283603,"uid":128570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T03:28:34.000Z","msg":"仲有呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/profile.php?id=1430830230483168\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fprofile.php%3Fid%3D1430830230483168&d=U4JEvS4lHdpitRbH3ga0O73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=6bbea113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/profile.php?i